Title: Hans
Descriptions: Sebastian: Hans made it back to Sanctuary in one piece. He's taken one of the bunks over in the rest area past the games machine - go and speak to him when you find time, he wants to say thanks - and he might have some work for you if you're interested.

Sebastian: Hans made it back to Sanctuary in one piece. He's taken one of the bunks over in the rest area past the games machine - go and speak to him when you find time, he wants to say thanks - and he might have some work for you if you're interested.

Hans: You saved me, survivor. I'll forever be in your debt. That Yellow King was a bastard. We're all grateful for your work in taking him out. Now that I'm back in Sanctuary Sebastian has tasked me with keeping a few important things in order. Check back with me regularly if you need some work - it pays well. Oh, and hey - take this. I found it on my way back to Sanctuary. There's something written on the back about some treasure, but I can't leave my station, so it's no use to me.
